{\fonttbl{\f0 Segoe UI;}}
\fs28\b Wisperlow installs everything needed for local dictation.\b0\par
\par
\fs20 \bullet  Press Ctrl + Alt + P to start or stop dictation.\par
\bullet  A small waveform pill appears while listening.\par
\bullet  Speech is transcribed locally with a bundled Whisper model.\par
\bullet  The final transcript is cleaned and pasted into the active text field.\par
\bullet  Optional Ollama support improves rewriting when installed locally.\par
\par
Audio stays on this computer by default. Cloud models are not required for the core experience.\par
